==Career== Imamo has played for [[Savigny-le-Temple FC|Savigny-le-Temple]], [[ALC Longvic|Longvic]], [[AS Quétigny|Quétigny]] and [[SC Selongey|Selongey]].<ref name = "NFT">{{NFT player|pid=65814|accessdate=3 June 2017}}</ref><ref>{{soccerway|abdallah-imamo-ahmed/456624|accessdate=3 June 2017}}</ref>
He made his international debut for [[Comoros national football team|Comoros]] in 2016.<ref name = "NFT"/>
