'''Al-Yarmouk FC''' ({{lang-ar|'''نادي اليرموك الرياضي'''}}) is [[Jordan]] a [[Association football|football]], formed in [[Amman]] in 1967, the club is currently part of the [[Jordan Premier League]].<ref>[http://www.civilsociety-jo.net/ar/organization/1853/%D9%86%D8%A7%D8%AF%D9%8A-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%8A%D8%B1%D9%85%D9%88%D9%83-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D8%B1%D8%AF%D9%86%D9%8A]</ref>

