::[[2005 CFU Club Championship|2005]]&nbsp;– Quarter-Finals&nbsp;— Lost against {{flagicon|Netherlands Antilles}} [[Centro Social Deportivo Barber]] 7&nbsp;– 3 on aggregate
::[[2007 CFU Club Championship|2007]]&nbsp;– Quarter-Finals&nbsp;— Lost against {{flagicon|Trinidad and Tobago}} [[Joe Public F.C.]] 4&nbsp;– 0

