[[Image:Club Hípico de Concepción (emblem).png|right]]

'''Club Hipico de Concepcion''', also called the '''Mediocamino''', is a [[Thoroughbred]] [[race track]] in [[Hualpen]] near [[Concepción, Chile|Concepcion]] in the [[Bio-Bio Region]] of [[Chile]]. It features a right-handed nine-furlong dirt track. Currently, no major races are run at the Mediocamino.

Four-time American Champion jockey [[Jose Santos]], a native of Concepcion, started his career at the track.

==External links==
