{{unref|date=December 2006}}
'''El Sekka El Hadid Stadium''' ({{lang-ar|ستاد السكة الحديد}}), also known as '''Railway Stadium''', is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Cairo]], [[Egypt]]. It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home of [[El Sekka El Hadid SC|El Sekka El Hadid]]. The stadium holds 25,000 people.

