'''Houssein Djama''' (born 23 July 1968) is a [[Djibouti]]an [[middle-distance running|middle-distance]] athlete.

Djama competed for his country at the [[1992 Summer Olympics]] held in [[Barcelona]], he entered the [[Athletics at the 1992 Summer Olympics – Men's 1500 metres|1500 metres]] where he came seventh in his heat so did not qualify for the next round.<ref>[https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/dj/houssein-djama-1.html Sports Reference Profile] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151001112715/http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/dj/houssein-djama-1.html |date=2015-10-01 }}</ref>

