{{infobox country at games | NPC = IRL | NPCname = [[Paralympics Ireland]] | games = Summer Paralympics | year = 1992 | flagcaption = | oldcode = | website = {{url|www.paralympics.ie }} | location = [[Barcelona]] | competitors = 58 | sports = | flagbearer = | rank = 43 | gold = 0 | silver = 3 | bronze = 4 | officials = | appearances = auto | app_begin_year = | app_end_year = | summerappearances = | winterappearances = | seealso = }} '''[[Ireland]]''' competed at the '''[[1992 Summer Paralympics]]''' in [[Barcelona]], [[Spain]]. 58 competitors from Ireland won 7 medals including 3 silver and 4 bronze and finished 43rd in the [[1992 Summer Paralympics medal table|medal table]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.paralympic.org/ireland|title=Ireland - National Paralympic Committee|website=www.paralympic.org|access-date=2016-06-13}}</ref>
