{{infobox country at games | NOC = PAN | NOCname = Comité Olímpico de Panamá | games = Summer Olympics | year = 1952 | flagcaption = | oldcode = | website = {{url|www.copanama.com }}&nbsp;{{es icon}} | location = [[Helsinki]] | competitors = | sports = | flagbearer = | rank = | gold = 0 | silver = 0 | bronze = 0 | officials = | appearances = auto | app_begin_year = | app_end_year = | summerappearances = | winterappearances = | seealso = }}
'''[[Panama]]''' competed at the '''[[1952 Summer Olympics]]''' in [[Helsinki]], [[Finland]]. It was the nations third time competing in the Olympics since 1928.
