{{Infobox football biography | name = Taufik Hidayat | image = | fullname = Taufik Hidayat | caption = | birth_date = {{bda|df=y|1993|3|20}} | birth_place = [[Demak, Indonesia]] | height = {{height|m=1.67}} | currentclub = [[Bali United F.C.|Bali United]] | clubnumber = 62 | position = [[Defender (association football)#Full-back|Full-back]] | youthyears1 = 2011–2012 | youthclubs1 = [[Persib U-21]] | youthyears2 = 2013 | youthclubs2 = PS Beltim U-21 | years1 = 2014–2017 | clubs1 = [[PSIS Semarang]] | caps1 = 19 | goals1 = 1 | years2 = 2017– | clubs2 = [[Bali United F.C.|Bali United]] | caps2 = 17 | goals2 = 0 | nationalyears1 = | nationalteam1 = | nationalcaps1 = | nationalgoals1 = | club-update = 2 December 2018 | ntupdate = }}
'''Taufik Hidayat''' (born in March 20, 1993) is an [[Indonesia]]n professional [[football (soccer)|football]] player who currently plays as a [[Defender (association football)#Full-back|Full-back]] for [[Liga 1 (Indonesia)|Liga 1]] club [[Bali United F.C.|Bali United]].<ref name="bu">{{cite web|title=RESMI! TAUFIK HIDAYAT JADI REKRUTAN TERBARU TIM SERDADU TRIDATU {{!}} Bali United Official Website|url=http://www.baliutd.com/news/media-news/resmi-taufik-hidayat-jadi-rekrutan-terbaru-tim-serdadu-tridatu/?ids=|website=Bali United Official Website|accessdate=17 December 2017|date=17 December 2017}}</ref>
==Career== ===PSIS Semarang=== First professional club of Taufik Hidayat was [[PSIS Semarang]]. Since the first year, Taufik was often being the first choice of coach. In the "Sepak Bola Gajah" scandal in 2014, Taufik received a five-year ban on playing in the league and fined Rp 50 million. But then in 2017 through Letter Number 009/Kep/PK-PSSI/I/2017 dated January 10, 2017, status of Taufik together with 9 players and three officials restored by PSSI.<ref>{{cite web|last1=TNR|first1=Nurdin Saleh|title=10 Pemain PSIS Dibebaskan dari Sanksi Kasus Sepak Bola Gajah|url=https://bola.tempo.co/read/839057/10-pemain-psis-dibebaskan-dari-sanksi-kasus-sepak-bola-gajah|website=Tempo|language=id-ID}}</ref>
===Bali United=== On December 17, 2017, he signed a year contract with [[Bali United F.C.|Bali United]].<ref name="bu"/>
